snippet.title: Sonic Advance Revamped SAGE 2017 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Sonic Advance Revamped is returning with a new engine, new features, new music, and more with a Special Demo set to debut at SAGE 2017!! 

Trailer Recorded and Edited by Garrulous64
https://www.youtube.com/user/MarioMasterDT

Custom Music Composed by AshZone
https://soundcloud.com/ashmusiczone

Game Logo Designed by MegapiCentral
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDwtc6h9O7KsITaax4uKm8w

Other Links:
https://discord.gg/aT2m6Jk
